 English and please be patiently with me if I get something wrong. \r\n\r\nIt's not possible to choose apc as session handler if you are running php >= 7.0\r\nI think this is caused by `libraries/vendor/joomla/session/Joomla/Session/Storage/Apc.php`,\r\nwhich this function has for detecting apc/apcu:\r\n\r\n```php\r\npublic static function isSupported()\r\n        {\r\n                return extension_loaded('apc');\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n\r\nTo support php >= 7.0 it should be:\r\n\r\n```php\r\npublic static function isSupported()\r\n        {\r\n                return extension_loaded('apcu');\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n\r\nOr we need an extra handler like already done in Joomla 4 with ``libraries/vendor/joomla/session/src/Handler/ApcHandler.php``  \r\n\r\nBest regards\r\nFelix","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/19939","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joomla/joomla-cms","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/19939/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/19939/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/19939/events","html_url":"https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/19939","id":306366009,"number":19939,"title":"Adding code to create databases breaks the installation script","user":{"login":"Texpaok","id":14203040,"avatar_url":"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/14203040?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Texpaok","html_url":"https://github.com/Texpaok","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Texpaok/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Texpaok/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Texpaok/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Texpaok/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Texpaok/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Texpaok/orgs","repos_u